      "name": "Kimsuky",
      "description": "North Korean state-sponsored threat actor also tracked as APT43, Velvet Chollima, Black Banshee, Thallium. Conducts cyber espionage targeting South Korean government, academic, and think-tank organizations. This campaign shows potential geographic expansion with Bulgarian-language invoice lures.",
